Module nl.naturalis.common

Java module containing basic language extensions and utility classes. The module is designed to be self-contained and have a small footprint. It has zero dependencies outside the java. namespace. It avoids as much as possible replicating functionality already present in libraries such as Apache Commons and Google Guava, but since it is designed to be self-contained, some overlap in inevitable.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
